0.1.name: wordpress/ibnfeed
0.1.description: This plugin will consume the XML feed of sessions which have been marked as 'Active', 'Session is public' and has 'Allow new participants' checked on the session record. This is managed from the 'Options' tab in the 'Session management' form inside of itsbooked.net.
